reviews.review_text:
Crispy This show has many great AUD's out there, and this one takes its place near the top.  Great sound here.  The show?  First set is an absolute BEAST.  From the Jack Straw opener all the way through the supernova Deal, this does not let up.  One of my faves end to end.  Second set is somewhat disappointing after that first, but still strong.
Recording Quality: 5 Stars
Show Quality: 4 Stars (8 for the first and 3 for the second)
Best source This is the best sounding version of this show, hands down.
